      "_value": "Let's go to #p218# in #m10001000#."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I ran into that same teddy-bear-costume-wearing #p218# at the #m10001050#. I did her a favor and took care of the #o16#s before. This time, she wants to make a claw as a present for a friend in #m10002000# who wants to go out on a journey. The claw she wants to make requires #b15 #t4010104#s, 30 #t4000050#s, and 30 #t4003000#s#k... If I get her all these... am I going to be richly rewarded?"
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#p218# asked me to get a gift for her friend who decided to set out on an adventure, and I brought it back for her. But it seems this alone isn’t enough."
