  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh, you're the one who beat the #o16#s for me~ You look much stronger than before? Did my scroll help you? Hehe... Anyway, good. Since you look strong, I would like to ask you a favor... Will you help me?"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "One of my friends in #m10002000# wants to be a adventurer. After some training, he will start traveling... I would like to give him something special! So I asked #p401# in #m10003000# to make a good claw and he wanted some weird stuff to make it."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "So can you get the materials #p401# wants? I'd like to get them by myself, but I can't move because of these stupid clothes! Of course, I will pay you if you do this for me... If you're not busy, can you please help me?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thanks! I need #b15 #t4010104#s, 30 #t4000050#s, and 30 #t4003000#s#k. Then I’ll leave it to you!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "You must be very busy... If you have time later, please get back to me~! My friend will start traveling soon..."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "It's the perfect time of year for an adventure!"
